{"tid":1254661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中文系請入]需要你地支筆！挽救香港！！！","createTime":"2019-06-24T08:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T08:44:06.000Z","uid":261627,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"080bcf91233517887cfac03beab482aeab2b8cfd","tid":1254661,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:32:23.000Z","msg":"見到連登有幾個留言，覺得可以試，但憑我嘅力量做唔到，作文叻，綜合卷叻嘅幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n我地需要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一封致香港人的道歉信</strong></span></span><br />\n建議內容(我冇乜文化，請大家補充):<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">温情，無奈，迫不得以，衷心道歉，我地都犧牲好多時間金錢甚至更多其他野，唔知可以做d乜，希望能支持626行動</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">動之以情，唔洗用靚字</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一封比政府嘅投訴信</span></strong></span><br />\n內容:<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">綜合連日以來示威者所受的苦，政府的無情， 虛偽嘅道歉，無視市民.... </span></span><br />\n<br />\n想法:<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">道歉信同投訴信一人印一封625要出到街</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>道歉信一路行派比受影響商戶/市民(鬧我地果d)，可能行之前夾咗喺傳媒鏡下show同埋大家<br />\n一齊道歉</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n投訴信就揀一個地方(政總，警總/立法會門口堆滿</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n用最溫柔的方法扭轉民意，btw我 dm咗鄺神，但唔知佢出唔出得切/做唔做，跪求文筆好嘅幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ba15e799ffcdc9414f90cffdc1f54dcef2ead9","tid":1254661,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:33:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8ff9324c8a2b9fb358c2779e7ebfd25d1d4abc36","tid":1254661,"uid":261627,"like":0,"